# 2026-05-18: file-logger output directory. Server writes
# `server-<date>.log` here in dev; cli writes here when
# SYSFLOW_LOG_DIR is pointed at the repo. Ignore the whole dir so
# any README / structure inside doesn't accidentally get committed.
.sysflow-logs/

